videos.headline: P. Nelson pass,to J. Summers for 4 yds for a TD
videos.description: Philip Nelson pass complete to James Summers for 4 yds for a TD

videos.headline: East Carolina scores on trick play
videos.description: East Carolina's wide receiver James Summers takes the snap, hands the reverse to receiver Zay Jones who throws it for the touchdown to quarterback Philip Nelson to put the Pirates up 14-3 over Connecticut.

videos.headline: East Carolina's offensive trickery pays off again
videos.description: East Carolina's offense reaches deep into its bag of tricks once again, with RB James Summers taking the pitch and then hitting Jimmy Williams for the 31-yard touchdown.
